{"tid":701162,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"保母車大圍收唔切 撞傷老翁","createTime":"2018-06-14T02:15:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-14T04:35:42.000Z","uid":122,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"8a5f5b5a4749352006e7ae3b81d289e38c4c144f","tid":701162,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T02:15:45.000Z","msg":"早上8時半許，一對老夫婦在大圍美松苑對開美田路橫過馬路時，一輛載有9名學童的保母車沿美田路駛至，<span style=\"color: red;\">老婦見狀即時停在路邊，但老翁卻仍衝出馬路</span>，結果被收掣不及的保母車撞倒受傷，救護員接報到場，將仍然清醒的老翁送院治理，警方經調查後，將保母車司機帶走。據悉，<span style=\"color: red;\">老翁橫過馬路的地方，並非在行人過路處</span>。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180614/58315995\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180614%2F58315995&d=jSaVrvWmoXwvmhgKSppV0zA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=be86ca32\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180614%2F58315995&h=28f4233d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180614/58315995</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/ifuf3RAbccnh6/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2Fifuf3RAbccnh6%2Fgiphy.gif&h=7607a13e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c891e1b744479595422c06c33d639f65ec561086","tid":701162,"uid":185656,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T02:16:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1743c5e65735ef62114f61559ec75a4ef0a738fd","tid":701162,"uid":170733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T02:17:27.000Z","msg":"又係死廢老<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8aa51dddfb2dbc5e4b9eefe3ef3f952e7dd24eb9","tid":701162,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T03:40:30.000Z","msg":"今晨8時19分，一對年長夫婦於大圍美田路近美松苑對開過馬路時，87歲老翁遭一輛駛至保母車撞倒，傷重昏迷地上，救護車趕至將傷者送院搶救後，惜告不治。警員在場調查，並向年約50歲司機了解意外經過，意外時保母車載有9名學童，稍後已由其他車輛接走，現場路面留下一攤血漬，距離約10米有行人過路處。經調查後，保母車司機涉嫌危險駕駛導致他人死亡被捕，帶返警署扣查，而涉事小巴拖走扣驗。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，老翁當時急步過馬路，並由保母車右至左走過。多名親友趕到醫院，死者女兒及女婿顯得情緒激動，並一度與調查的警員爭拗。"},{"pid":"821bf27ef030f925856b443c6f56084a28d67b63","tid":701162,"uid":57840,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T03:46:04.000Z","msg":"司機被佢害撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92271257646865860fd6a42c35b70eccbe2ab2a2","tid":701162,"uid":164913,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T04:08:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1864aa42a206c320831e6ec5d256f11f646f71c3","tid":701162,"uid":187076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T04:10:59.000Z","msg":"老人家好中意亂過馬路"},{"pid":"20bed27fd227614a6b62d8404a9ae21af3ccc1e1","tid":701162,"uid":17765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T04:12:45.000Z","msg":"佢老婆咁撚醒 嫁著個咁撚蠢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"827bdd1a1e39ee2e98e98948a029833f4819ec9c","tid":701162,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1864aa42a206c320831e6ec5d256f11f646f71c3","tid":701162,"uid":187076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T04:10:59.000Z","msg":"老人家好中意亂過馬路"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T04:35:42.000Z","msg":"以後唔會架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}